name: Webflow Starter UI Kit
description:
I wanted to create a UI Kit that helps you start out any Webflow project. This contains many of the default styles and layouts that you can expect to see when adding elements to your projects.


Have suggestions? Let me know! @designerbrett on Twitter.


v1.1 - Added updates with Variants to the form components. Fixed an error on the dropdown link item. The header in the Prebuilt Layouts is also scaleable now.
